        <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-[0.95rem] text-muted-text">The core Bessel-mode displacement function mapping radius, angle, and a mode index to surface displacement. This is the heart of every colored triangle on the cone mesh.</p>
        <div class="mt-8">
